29
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:49,610
It hurts.

30
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:50,760
What?

31
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,800
Now you know what pain feels like?

32
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,480
I have to tie you up like a criminal

33
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,410
so I can take you to see Master Chen.

34
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,760
I said you could tie me up,

35
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:01,320
but I didn't say you could tie me this tight.

36
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,480
If I don't tie you up tightly,

37
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,280
what if

38
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,060
you try to assassinate

39
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,720
Master Chen when you see him?

40
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:13,290
Let's go.

41
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,000
Li Ling.

42
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,680
I told you to catch a thief,

43
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,340
why did you bring back a woman?

44
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:26,840
This young lady's identity is suspicious.

45
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:29,170
Blood stains were found at her residence.

46
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,760
Madam,

47
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,850
I've been wrongfully accused!

48
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,040
I am a physician

49
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,600
who runs a clinic in Huaiyuan District.

50
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:39,480
Patients come and go every day,

51
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:42,050
and some inevitably bleed from their wounds.

52
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,360
There's a war outside the city.

53
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,160
Those wounded soldiers

54
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,890
often come to me for treatment.

55
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:50,440
It's unavoidable to have bloodstains inside and outside my place.

56
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,120
I certainly haven't

57
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,120
done anything terrible!

58
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:54,680
[Pleading]

59
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,280
If you don't believe me,

60
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,560
