71
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,880
My name is Nongyu,

72
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,300
I'm from Shanzhou.

73
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,600
I've studied medicine since childhood

74
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,399
and traveled throughout the Western Regions.

75
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:23,460
I just arrived in Chang'an recently.

76
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,740
From the west, huh?

77
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,640
You, a mere woman,

78
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,290
You really are a doctor.

79
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:34,000
If you don't believe me, I can prove myself.

80
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:39,780
The medicinal fragrance in this room...

81
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:42,400
has the scent of Chuanxiong and Zhuyu.

82
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,200
These two herbs

83
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,330
are often used to treat headaches.

84
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,240
I dare to guess

85
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,640
that you suffer from headaches.

86
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:56,170
Do you experience insomnia and night sweats?

87
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,960
How did you know that?

88
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,760
This prescription may relieve headaches,

89
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,760
but it cannot cure the root cause.

90
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:05,880
If used for too long,

91
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:07,140
it will harm your body.

92
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,610
So you're saying

93
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,370
you have a better solution?

94
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,690
I dare to take your pulse, Sir Chen.

95
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:18,730
Sir Chen,

96
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,570
