97
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,360
This woman's background is unknown.

98
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,320
It could be dangerous to let her get close.

99
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,760
Officer Li, why would you say such things?

100
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:28,720
How could anyone dare to harm someone of Sir Chen's status?

101
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,520
I don't need to get close.

102
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:31,640
I can still take your pulse from a distance.

103
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,600
Is that true?

104
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,080
How extraordinary!

105
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:54,159
Years ago in the palace, I only saw once

106
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:59,300
when Master Yun diagnosed the Imperial Consort using suspended thread pulse-taking.

107
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:03,120
I already understand your condition, sir.

108
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,880
I'll prepare the medicine for you right away.

109
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:07,640
Li Ling

110
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:08,380
is here.

111
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,040
Assist me

112
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,640
and make no mistakes.

113
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,360
Yes.

114
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,610
Your medicine better work.

115
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,820
Otherwise, in this Huaiyuan clinic,

116
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:21,280
