122
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,560
It's arranged by Officer Li.

123
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,410
Please come in, gentlemen.

124
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:12,530
Come.

125
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:23,000
Quickly prepare the medicine according to this prescription.

126
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,640
